title: HOUR 1- Pat Forde Sep 17, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Pat Forde Sep 17, 2020
description:
Pat Forde and Dan discuss what happened to make the Big 10 decide to play football in the fall. Pat says rapid testing and seeing other teams playing football wore the college presidents down and persuaded them to change their minds.
